1601024400.descr: Early Start is a hard news morning television show on CNN anchored by Christine Romans and Laura Jarrett, aired weekdays. Keep up with the latest news and top stories of the day, stay tuned for all important events on the global arena.

1601038800.title: First Move with Julia Chatterley
1601038800.descr: First Move is a business news show,broadcast live daily from the floor of the New York Stock Exchange. The host of the show is Julia Chatterley, a global market analyst, an anchor and correspondent for CNN. The show highlights top stories in the world of business and money. Be the first to know the news influencing global politics, culture and finance.

1601056800.title: Amanpour
1601056800.descr: Christiane Amanpour provides her powerful interview skills and provocative analysis on global stories that matter to you.

1601060400.title: Quest Means Business
1601060400.descr: He's not messing around: Richard Quest presents his hot takes on the biggest breaking stories in the world of business. Watch for the expert analysis, commentary and opinions on the important headlines in the field from the notorious English journalist and CNN anchor. Joined by a cast of experts and correspondents delivering unrivaled facts on everything going down in the world of business.

1601064000.title: The Lead with Jake Tapper
1601064000.descr: Current affairs programme hosted by the journalist and author, Jake Tapper. Jake Tapper is the chief Washington correspondent for CNN and he will share his knowledge and insight into politics as well as covering a variety of other topics. This programme discusses a range of stories from topical events including national news, economics/finance, sports, health, technology and world affairs.

1601067600.title: The Situation Room
1601067600.descr: Wolf Blitzer is in the command center for breaking news, politics and extraordinary reports from around the world.

1601074800.title: Erin Burnett OutFront
1601074800.descr: Hosted by Erin Burnett, OutFront is an hour-long news programme examining the latest stories from the US and further afield. The show features insightful opinions from informed guests, leaving no stone unturned.

1601078400.title: Anderson Cooper 360
1601078400.descr: Anderson Cooper delves into the day's news, looking beyond the broadcast to give his take, prompting us to re-think what we hear in the headlines. Cooper has covered major, international stories like the aftermath of Hurricane Katrina on the Gulf Coast, the catastrophic BP oil spill and the 2010 earthquake in Haiti, which saw the whole world fall silent.

1601082000.title: Cuomo Prime Time
1601082000.descr: Chris Cuomo gets after it with newsmakers in Washington and around the world.

1601085600.title: CNN Tonight with Don Lemon
1601085600.descr: Late-night news programme brought to you by Don Lemon and the news team at CNN. Bringing you comprehensive coverage of news from the USA and around the world. This hour-long broadcast features analysis, opinion and insight on the day's top stories. Don Lemon is an award-winning American television journalist who joined CNN in 2006.
